This is your Play application
=============================

To run tests
-------------

sbt clean test

To run
-------

sbt run

Endpoints
==========

GET /items?details=true/false?start=""?size=0
returns all items that match criteria

GET /items/{id}
returns item with requested id

PUT /items/{id}
Example Request Payload:
|{
|  "id": 1,
|  "price": {
|    "value": 12,
|    "currency": "GBP"
|   },
|  "colour": {
|    "value": "colour"
|  },
|  "tags": {
|    "value": "tags"
|  },
|  "size": {
|    "value": 100,
|    "region": "EU"
|  },
|  "state": {
|    "value": "state"
|  },
|  "sku": {
|    "value": "sku"
|  }
|}

inserts or updates item with requested id

